title: Images of December
text:
Images of December   01:01 
Images taken by Reuters photographers around the world for the month of December 2017, including Palestinian protests over Trump's U.S. embassy move to Jerusalem, the Rohingya refugee crisis, Christmas celebrations and ringing in 2018. Produced by Canice Leung. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
